      <title>全球科技颠覆后，航空公司急于重回正轨</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/en/news/thp/2024-07-20/internet-outage-latest-airlines-rush-to-get-back-on-track-after-global-tech-disruption</link>
      <description><![CDATA[周六，由于大规模技术故障导致系统长时间中断，运输服务提供商、企业和政府正在争分夺秒恢复所有系统。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/en/news/thp/2024-07-20/internet-outage-latest-airlines-rush-to-get-back-on-track-after-global-tech-disruption</guid>
